abstract_ssm: The Greenwall Foundation's Arts and Humanities Program (1991-2011) supported arts organizations and emerging artists. This collection contains subject files of artists and organizations who applied for and/or received grants from the Greenwall Foundation. It also contains audiovisual media and objects that were the products of Greenwall grants.
